Tavole di mortalità

finf.lt <- lifetable(fin, series = names(fin$rate)[1], years = fin$year, ages = fin$age, max.age = min(110, max(fin$age)), type = c("period"))
finm.lt <- lifetable(fin, series = names(fin$rate)[2], years = fin$year, ages = fin$age, max.age = min(110, max(fin$age)), type = c("period"))
fint.lt <- lifetable(fin, series = names(fin$rate)[3], years = fin$year, ages = fin$age, max.age = min(110, max(fin$age)), type = c("period"))


lifetable_fem <- finf.lt
lifetable_mal <- finm.lt
lifetable_tot <- fint.lt
italyf.lt <- lifetable(italy, series = names(italy$rate)[1], years = italy$year, ages = italy$age, max.age = min(110, max(italy$age)), type = c("period"))
italym.lt <- lifetable(italy, series = names(italy$rate)[2], years = italy$year, ages = italy$age, max.age = min(110, max(italy$age)), type = c("period"))
italyt.lt <- lifetable(italy, series = names(italy$rate)[3], years = italy$year, ages = italy$age, max.age = min(110, max(italy$age)), type = c("period"))

Visualizzazione base

#log dei tassi di mortalità

plot(fin, series=names(fin$rate)[3], year=1900:2014, main="Finlandia 1900-2014")

plot(italy, series=names(italy$rate)[3], year=1900:2014, main="Italia 1900-2014")

#curve di sopravvivenza 3d
age <- fint.lt$age
year <- fint.lt$year
year <- year[-c(1:22)]
year <- year[-c(116)]
lx <- fint.lt$lx
lx <- lx[,-c(1:22,116)]

persp(age,year,lx, theta = 40, zlab = "lx", main = "Finlandia lx  1900-2014")

age_it <- italyt.lt$age
year_it <- italyt.lt$year
year_it <- year_it[-c(1:28)]
lx_it <- italyt.lt$lx[,-c(1:28)]

persp(age_it,year_it,lx_it, theta = 40, zlab = "lx",ylab = "year",xlab = "age", main = "Italia lx 1900-2014")

Aspettativa di vita

#importo
fin0 <- hmd.e0("FIN", "gabelfra1@hotmail.it", "superorso1")
ita0 <- hmd.e0("ITA", "gabelfra1@hotmail.it", "superorso1")
#grafico
fin0_tot <- fin0[,3]
fin0_tot <- fin0_tot[-c(1:22,116)]
ita0_tot <- ita0[,3]
ita0_tot <- ita0_tot[-c(1:28)]

plot(year,fin0_tot,main="Speranza di vita alla nascita Finlandia-Italia 1900-2014",type = "lines",ylab = "age")
## Warning in plot.xy(xy, type, ...): tipo lpot 'lines' verrà troncato al
## primo carattere
lines(year,ita0_tot,col="red")
legend("bottomright", inset=.05, title="Nazione",
    c("Finlandia","Italia"), fill=c("black","red"))
